						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is found by the side of an image (of the donor). The subject of the inscription is that Vijayarā(ya)r of Koṟṟamaṅgalam, made the gift of lands for performing <hi rend="italic">pūja</hi> and other sacred services in the temple at Tayiūr.</p>						

						</summary>
